  "instructions": [
    "Char the chilies over an open flame until blackened.",
    "Peel the charred chilies and remove the seeds.",
    "In a bain-marie, combine the peeled chilies, lime juice, fish sauce, and palm sugar.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until the sugar has dissolved.",
    "Mash the avocado in a bowl and stir in the chili mixture.",
    "Fold in the roasted peanuts, cherry tomatoes, and chopped cilantro.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the som tum immediately, garnished with additional cilantro if desired.",
    "Refrigerate any leftovers for up to a day.",
    "Reheat the som tum gently before serving."
